                           Alten Haid, die da stösset an den Abtsperg</roleName>, des <measure>fünf
                           achtail</measure> ist, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-immo_abtsperg_vor_stubentor_2">zenagst</roleName>
                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_abtsperg_vor_stubentor_2"><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__michael_paumgartner_QGW_II_II_2159"><rs type="person" ref="pe__michael_paumgartner_QGW_II_II_2159">Micheln
